snippet.title: BINI | 'Blink Twice' Official Music Video
snippet.description:
#BINI : ‘Blink Twice’ is a fun pop song about trying to figure out if your crush likes you back. With a catchy beat and relatable lyrics, it captures the excitement and confusion of waiting for a sign- like a simple blink- to know if they feel the same. 

Stream #BINI_BlinkTwice now on all platforms: https://orcd.co/bini_blinktwice 

I heard you like confidence
Well I’ve got a lot of it
So baby use common sense
Just don’t be anonymous
I heard that you’ve been busy
Yeah I heard it through the grapevine
Trying my best not to step up on your land mine
But let’s have some fun with it
Cause you know I’m running it

Ooh ooh
I’m lost inside your world
You got that symphony
Like da doo da doo da doo

If you like me blink twice
Are you naughty or nice
Maybe add a little spice
If you’re tryna roll the dice
Let me give you some advice
If you like me blink twice
Uh oh

Ooh ooh 
He’s not even thinkin’ bout me
Ooh ooh 
Maybe he’s just lookin’ at me

Got me goin’ crazy
Baby no don’t be lazy
Come over and chase me
Yeah you better amaze me
I’m at the spot
Baby tell me are you
Ready or not
Don’t you leave me waitin’

If you, you really like me
Baby then just blink twice
If you, you really like me
Then you gotta roll the dice

BINI is an 8-member girl group composed of young, modern Filipinas who aspire to share their talent & passion w/the world.

[शांत आइटम आधिकारिक] परिवार में शामिल हों और उन वस्तुओं का पता लगाएं और साझा करें जो जीवन को बेहतर बनाते हैं!🌈

सभी वीडियो मुख्य भूमि चीन के रचनाकारों द्वारा अधिकृत हैं और प्लेटफॉर्म नियमों का सख्ती से पालन करते हैं।🛡के

snippet.title: JAZZ at LAKERS | FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | February 10, 2025
snippet.description:
The Lakers defeated the Jazz, 132-113 tonight in Los Angeles. LeBron James contributed a team-high 24 points to go with 8 assists 7 rebounds and 3 three pointers, with Austin Reaves of the Lakers adding an additional 22 points (6-10 FG, 3-5 3P), 9 rebounds, and 4 assists in the game. Lauri Markkanen finished with a team-high 17 points along with 3 rebounds for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Lakers improve their record to 32-19 with the win, while the Jazz fall to 12-40 for the season. The teams will meet again in their next game on Wednesday, 2/12/2025, when the Jazz host the Lakers (9:00 PM ET, KJZZ/Spectrum SportsNet).

أي إجراء تقوم به بناءً على المعلومات الواردة في هذا الفيديو يكون على مسؤوليتك الشخصية، ولن نكون مسؤولين عن أي أضرار أو خسائر. من مسؤولية المشاهد استخدام الحكم والرعاية واتخاذ الاحتياطات إذا كان يخطط لتكرار ما يظهر في الفيديو.
